 a civil jury in [[Linden,_Texas|Linden, Texas]].<ref name=TexasMonthlyBRJ/><ref name="ChicagoTribuneBRJ"/><ref>{{Cite news | url=http://www.splcenter.org/news/item.jsp?aid=250 | title=Center Wins Justice for Billy Ray Johnson | publisher=Southern Poverty Law Center | date=April 20, 2007 | first= | last= | accessdate=2007-08-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070715062116/http://www.splcenter.org/news/item.jsp?aid=250 | archive-date=2007-07-15 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>陪审团希望这个裁决能够改善社区中的种族关系。在审判期间，一名被告，考瑞·希克斯(Cory Hicks)称约翰逊为“它”，这一带有侮辱性的字眼。<ref name="USATodayBRJ">{{Cite news | url=http://www.usatoday.com/news/nation/2007-04-26-texas-town_N.htm | title=A jury's stand against racism reflects hope | work=[[USA_Today|USA Today]] | date=April 26, 2007 | first=Laura | last=Parker | accessdate=2007-08-17 | archive-date=2012-08-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120812025347/http://www.usatoday.com/news/nation/2007-04-26-texas-town_N.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref>

====美国皇家三K党案件====
